Ngoài ra, hãy tạo file `.gitignore` trong thư mục gốc của dự án và thêm một số file `.gitignore` bổ sung trong các thư mục con:

## 1. File .gitignore trong thư mục app/

```gitignore:app/.gitignore
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Local configuration
config.py
secrets.py
.env

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
tmp/
temp/
```

## 2. File .gitignore trong thư mục tests/

```gitignore:tests/.gitignore
<code_block_to_apply_changes_from>
```

## 3. File .gitignore trong thư mục migrations/

```gitignore:migrations/.gitignore
# Generated migration files
versions/*.py
!versions/__init__.py

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
```

## 4. Tạo script để clean cache

```bash:scripts/clean.sh
#!/bin/bash

echo "🧹 Cleaning Python cache and temporary files..."

# Remove Python cache
find . -type d -name "__pycache__" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "*.pyc" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "*.pyo" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "*.pyd" -delete 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove test cache
find . -name ".pytest_cache" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name ".coverage" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "coverage.xml" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "htmlcov" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove mypy cache
find . -name ".mypy_cache" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove virtual environment cache
find . -name ".venv" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "venv" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove IDE cache
find . -name ".idea" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name ".vscode" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove OS cache
find . -name ".DS_Store" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "Thumbs.db" -delete 2>/dev/null || true

# Remove temporary files
find . -name "*.tmp" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "*.temp" -delete 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "tmp" -type d -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
find . -name "temp" -type d -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true

echo "✅ Cleanup completed!"
```

## 5. Cập nhật Makefile để thêm clean command

```makefile:Makefile
.PHONY: help install install-dev test test-coverage lint format clean clean-all docker-build docker-run deploy

help: ## Show this help message
	@echo 'Usage: make [target]'
	@echo ''
	@echo 'Targets:'
	@awk 'BEGIN {FS = ":.*?## "} /^[a-zA-Z_-]+:.*?## / {printf "  %-15s %s\n", $$1, $$2}' $(MAKEFILE_LIST)

install: ## Install production dependencies
	pip install -r requirements.txt

install-dev: ## Install development dependencies
	pip install -r requirements.txt
	pip install -r requirements-dev.txt

test: ## Run tests
	pytest tests/ -v

test-coverage: ## Run tests with coverage report
	pytest tests/ -v --cov=app --cov-report=html --cov-report=term-missing --cov-fail-under=80

test-fast: ## Run only fast tests
	pytest tests/ -v -m "not slow"

test-unit: ## Run only unit tests
	pytest tests/ -v -m "unit"

test-integration: ## Run only integration tests
	pytest tests/ -v -m "integration"

lint: ## Run linting
	flake8 app/ tests/
	black --check app/ tests/
	isort --check-only app/ tests/

format: ## Format code
	black app/ tests/
	isort app/ tests/

clean: ## Clean up Python cache and test artifacts
	find . -type f -name "*.pyc" -delete
	find . -type d -name "__pycache__" -delete
	find . -name ".pytest_cache" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
	rm -rf .coverage htmlcov/ .mypy_cache/

clean-all: ## Clean all cache, temporary files and build artifacts
	@echo " Cleaning all cache and temporary files..."
	@if [ -f scripts/clean.sh ]; then bash scripts/clean.sh; else echo "Clean script not found"; fi
	find . -type f -name "*.pyc" -delete
	find . -type d -name "__pycache__" -delete
	find . -name ".pytest_cache" -exec rm -rf {} + 2>/dev/null || true
	rm -rf .coverage htmlcov/ .mypy_cache/ build/ dist/ *.egg-info/

docker-build: ## Build Docker image
	docker build -t digital-library .

docker-run: ## Run Docker container
	docker run -p 5000:5000 digital-library

deploy: ## Deploy to production
	kubectl apply -f k8s/

migrate: ## Run database migrations
	alembic upgrade head

seed: ## Seed database with sample data
	python scripts/seed_data.py

pre-commit: ## Run pre-commit hooks
	pre-commit run --all-files

security-check: ## Run security checks
	bandit -r app/
	safety check

fresh-start: clean-all install-dev ## Clean everything and reinstall dependencies
	@echo "🚀 Fresh start completed!"
```

## 6. Tạo .gitattributes để xử lý line endings

```gitattributes:.gitattributes
# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

# Python files
*.py text eol=lf

# Shell scripts
*.sh text eol=lf

# YAML files
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

# Markdown files
*.md text eol=lf

# Configuration files
*.ini text eol=lf
*.cfg text eol=lf
*.conf text eol=lf

# Documentation
*.txt text eol=lf
*.rst text eol=lf

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.db binary
*.sqlite binary
*.sqlite3 binary
```

Bây giờ bạn có thể:

1. **Chạy cleanup**: `make clean-all` hoặc `bash scripts/clean.sh`
2. **Git sẽ ignore tất cả cache files** và file tự sinh
3. **Không còn file cache nào** được commit vào repository

Sau khi cập nhật `.gitignore`, hãy chạy:

```bash
# Xóa tất cả cache files hiện tại
make clean-all

# Commit thay đổi
git add .gitignore .gitattributes scripts/clean.sh
git commit -m "chore: Update gitignore and add cleanup scripts"

# Push để trigger CI/CD
git push origin your-branch
```

Bây giờ CI/CD sẽ chạy sạch sẽ và không còn file cache nào được commit!
